simple binder is a minimalistic implementation of Android binder kernel module
Only basic feature of binder are implemented

Basic Architect

simple_binder.c
	kernel module facilitate binder transaction between binder client-service

service_manager.cpp
	binder context manager used to store all binder server register

binder_server.c
	example of a binder server registered as name "echo"

binder_client.c
	example of binder client connect to binder_server and execute IPC method


Usage
	1.make
	2.open new shell and install simple_binder kernel module "sudo insmod simple_binder.ko"
	3.open another shell and run service_manager "sudo ./service_manager"
	4.open another shell and run binder_server "sudo ./binder_server"
	5.open another shell and run binder_client "sudo ./binder_client"
